  "text": "Testes were stained as described [CITATION_1] , incorporating an additional 1h permeabilization step with 1% Triton X-100 following fixation. The following antisera were used: rat-anti-DECadherin (DSHB, DCAD2) 1:100, mouse-anti-Eya (DSHB, eya10H6) 1:20, mouse-anti-FasIII (DSHB, 7G10) 1:100, rabbit-anti-GFP (Clontech) 1:500, rabbit-anti-Kibra (Nic Tapon) 1:200, rat-anti-Tj (Dorothea Godt) 1:250, Rabbit anti-vasa (Paul Lasko) 1:5000, rabbit-anti-Zfh1 (Ruth Lehmann) 1:4000. Secondary ABs raised in goat and labelled with (Invitrogen) were used 1:500.",
